  "detailed_description": "<h1>Also recommended for you</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1676154409\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1676154409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1676154409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Six Faces | Overpower</h2>Step up to the challenge and test your skills with responsive controls and extremely difficult puzzles. Six faces, four powers (🚀,📦,💣,⚓). Easy to learn, hard to master, with 64 hand-drawn puzzles to solve. Unleash your creativity and dive into a world of fun with tons of alternate mechanics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Effortless and Engaging Controls for Maximum Fun: Enjoy a game that's easy to play and responsive.<br></li><li> Explore multiple visuals from different worlds<br></li><li> Challenging Combinations of Different Powers: Learn and feel challenged with unique powers and their incredible combinations.<br></li><li> Innovative Mechanics that Make the Game Even More Fun and Exciting<br></li><li> Solve All 64 Hand-Drawn Puzzles (if You Can).</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Powers</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HOOK</h2>Reach distant places, pull objects, and more<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/3a74ece811f601316e856b9ca66b4bfb.poster.avif?t=1676154409\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/3a74ece811f601316e856b9ca66b4bfb.webm?t=1676154409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/3a74ece811f601316e856b9ca66b4bfb.mp4?t=1676154409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ROCKET</h2>Boost yourself in any of the six directions<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/cd8624fd4547dbdacacb40ab6d96dc1c.poster.avif?t=1676154409\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/cd8624fd4547dbdacacb40ab6d96dc1c.webm?t=1676154409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/cd8624fd4547dbdacacb40ab6d96dc1c.mp4?t=1676154409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BOMB</h2>Blast the obstacles and advance in level<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/2f4be6185397c02f7b32687a3cfaf4b7.poster.avif?t=1676154409\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/2f4be6185397c02f7b32687a3cfaf4b7.webm?t=1676154409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/2f4be6185397c02f7b32687a3cfaf4b7.mp4?t=1676154409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREATOR</h2>Create blocks at the right time and complete new challenges<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799020/extras/503c20f79